    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the person i actually was... the one with all the plans and the spark... died a long time ago. i'm just going through the motions now. like a ghost haunting my own life.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
