      "content": "It's a heavy feeling to carry, but you are not alone in this; many people feel like ghosts in their own lives when the spark fades. The person you remember isn't gone, but they are hiding behind the exhaustion and the weight of the world, and you are just as real as they were. Sometimes, the only way to find that spark again is to stop trying to force it and instead let go of the heavy expectations you've been holding onto.",
